          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1585746835966-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pasta has been cooking for 7 min, add the<strong> halved</strong> <strong>asparagus</strong> and <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further or until just tender</p><p>Once tender, drain and return to the pot, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1585746846225-x200.jpg",
